name: tired pixels #16
description: The book of life has already been written. You are already dead. Right now you are turning the pages of life. Read carefully! There is a chance to see frame 25 between the lines. However, I am not interested in books. I'm interested in the one who has these books on the shelf. Absolute. Ohm
